
    <h2>How to Take Good Care of Your Cat</h2>

    <h4>1. Encourage the cat to use a litter box.</h4>
    <h4>2. Make the litter box a comfortable place.</h4>
    <h4>3. Take young or old cats needs into consideration.</h4>
    <h4>4. Provide the cat with a scratching post.</h4>
    <h4>5. Discourage the cat from exploring forbidden surfaces.</h4>
    <h4>6. Consider using feline pheromone products.</h4>
